{"tid":669660,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果投胎有得俾你二選一，你想做 澤鉅 定係澤楷","createTime":"2018-05-18T15:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T00:30:24.000Z","uid":5584,"like":12,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"226243c1213553ea2f7614c2e6a806d80d46e3a2","tid":669660,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"只可二個選一個<br />\n冇其他選擇<br />\n你會點㨂<br />\n有咩原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澤鉅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澤楷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996953af11e23581f2be52d90501f27465d8ba33","tid":669660,"uid":170270,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"e2f9551219cdf3d6186a53746a4fd461de7ebd9c","tid":669660,"uid":119695,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"我想做澤使"},{"pid":"1eb84d5dc9c13a0079cef6d80f096243c8a767c8","tid":669660,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"話說某城市一有名富豪年青時工作極度勤奮，經常癈寢忘餐，連屋企都冇時間日日返。<br />\n<br />\n佢太太第一胎臨盆時，佢正在公司煩惱一單大生意的計劃。<br />\n<br />\nＢＢ生出，係仔，太太即叫管家去搵老爺幫個仔改名，管家即時去老爺公司搵佢，告之太太母子平安&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n管：老爺，太太生咗個仔。<br />\n<br />\n富：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n管：太太想我問你少爺個名，由老爺你作主改名。<br />\n<br />\n富：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;（煩惱工作中&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;）<br />\n<br />\n管：老爺，太太佢&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n富：咩呀！理柒佢呀！！（有少少外省鄉音）<br />\n<br />\n之後，老管家便帶住少爺個名給太太；叫『宅巨』<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到第二胎太太臨盆時，富豪正在招呼一單大生意嘅客人喺酒家中用膳。<br />\n<br />\nＢＢ出世，又係仔，太太同様叫管家去搵老爺幫個仔改名。<br />\n<br />\n管家今次學精咗，唔再直接親身搵老爺，怕阻礙佢工作，打流動電話去搵老爺&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n富：喂。<br />\n<br />\n管：老爺，太太生咗個仔。<br />\n<br />\n富：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;（背景係酒家熱鬧聲音，老爺似乎招呼緊，同緊其他人講嘢&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;）<br />\n<br />\n管: 太太想我問你少爺個名。<br />\n<br />\n富：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;（背景係酒家熱鬧聲音，老爺聲音好似唔喺電話聽筒邊）<br />\n<br />\n管: 老爺，太太佢&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n富：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;食雞，食雞&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; （有些少潮州口音，廣東話聽似『吔雞』&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;可能招呼緊客人）<br />\n<br />\n之後，老管家就帶住少爺個新名畀太太，叫『宅佳』。"},{"pid":"563c2244ac634034121611bd0fbbd686410d5217","tid":669660,"uid":59711,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"要是能重來，我要選李白"},{"pid":"120dc0ac811e98f000d3b89435e19ea3ab475810","tid":669660,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"求撚其啦"},{"pid":"0192887b639d874f89eb23ee270a2e195d9e0ce5","tid":669660,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"澤鉅"},{"pid":"3e1cf31ccfc812d11c8986b0f4e6c28fd152ec15","tid":669660,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"996953af11e23581f2be52d90501f27465d8ba33","tid":669660,"uid":170270,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"92b458898ad14bba3c17b0091ff92bd49b3fecb4","tid":669660,"uid":165156,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"有+x做daddy叫我澤屌都冇所謂"},{"pid":"35d9cf19159039ee451810afa77ec44d65f41a5f","tid":669660,"uid":83527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"澤西哥"},{"pid":"6bca5dfcafcf63d2fd44845ffccd407bf1d999e8","tid":669660,"uid":5893,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1eb84d5dc9c13a0079cef6d80f096243c8a767c8","tid":669660,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"話說某城市一有名富豪年青時工作極度勤奮，經常癈寢忘餐，連屋企都冇時間日日返。<br />\n<br />\n佢太太第一胎臨盆時，佢正在公司煩惱一單大生意的計劃。<br />\n<br />\nＢＢ生出，係仔，太太即叫管家去搵老爺幫個仔改名，管家即時去老爺公司搵佢，告之太太母子平安&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />